  "texts": [
    "For example, realistic details from the deformed clothing have been exploited by a network to render blurred regions (Han et al. 2018).",
    "In the same vein, Ge et al. (2021b) used warped clothes, human pose estimation, and reserved regions on the human body as input.",
    "They combined Res-UNet with residual connections to preserve the details of the deformed clothes and to generate realistic fitting results.",
    "A virtual try-on task can also replace a target garment on a person with the target model.",
    "This task focuses on transferring the clothes worn in the original image C o onto arbitrary model images m a, rather than requiring clean product images."
